Trainers

Savage and the other Trainers arrived at their destination, turning 
on their cloaking devices. Prebon, with Spears by his side, arrived 
at the meeting place. Prebon contacted Slayer.

"Slayer, are you in position on the cliff? We need you to come 
through on this."
